ODDCAT stands for Overdress & Copy That. And as we grow, we are slowly moving into “Overdress & Conscious At”. Consciously crafted “upcycled leather” bags and goods that are made from leftover leather skins in factories. Fabrics that are eco-friendly. We are making sure, we are “consciously” consuming fashion, one bag at a time. Join us in our journey and enjoy luxury that only spoils you, not your planet ♥️

ODD SERIES: What’s in your bag ?

Founder’s favourite- Red Globetrotter in reclaimed calf leather & also in certified #veganleather ! From laptop to iPad to notebook to phone to wallet to perfume to charger to water bottle to snack to keys to sunglasses to make up to other knick knacks, this one has it all.
And while it carries everything you desire, it looks chic while doing so. Comes with a detachable pouch to act as a travel wallet. It’s truly your BFF & comes in cool shade of red aka colour of the season 💁🏻‍♀️
